==English==

===Noun===
'''barber''' (''plural'' '''[[barbers]]''')

# A person whose profession is [[cut]]ting (usually male) customers' [[hair]] and [[beard]]s.

====Synonyms====
*[[hairdresser]], [[hair-dresser]]
*[[hairstylist]], [[hair-stylist]]

